{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Those of you who may remember me from TEDGlobal"},{"time":2000,"text":"remember me asking a few questions"},{"time":4000,"text":"which still preoccupy me."},{"time":6000,"text":"One of them was: Why is it necessary to spend"},{"time":8000,"text":"six billion pounds"},{"time":10000,"text":"speeding up the Eurostar train"},{"time":12000,"text":"when, for about 10 percent of that money,"},{"time":14000,"text":"you could have top supermodels, male and female,"},{"time":16000,"text":"serving free Chateau Petrus to all the passengers"},{"time":19000,"text":"for the entire duration of the journey?"},{"time":21000,"text":"You'd still have five billion left in change,"},{"time":23000,"text":"and people would ask for the trains to be slowed down."},{"time":26000,"text":"Now, you may remember me asking the question as well,"},{"time":28000,"text":"a very interesting observation,"},{"time":30000,"text":"that actually those strange little signs"},{"time":32000,"text":"that actually flash \"35\" at you,"},{"time":34000,"text":"occasionally accompanying a little smiley face"},{"time":36000,"text":"or a frown,"},{"time":38000,"text":"according to whether you're within or outside the speed limit --"},{"time":41000,"text":"those are actually more effective"},{"time":43000,"text":"at preventing road accidents than speed cameras,"},{"time":46000,"text":"which come with the actual threat"},{"time":48000,"text":"of real punishment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":50000,"text":"So there seems to be a strange disproportionality at work,"},{"time":53000,"text":"I think, in many areas of human problem solving,"},{"time":56000,"text":"particularly those which involve human psychology,"},{"time":59000,"text":"which is: The tendency"},{"time":61000,"text":"of the organization or the institution"},{"time":63000,"text":"is to deploy as much force as possible,"},{"time":66000,"text":"as much compulsion as possible,"},{"time":68000,"text":"whereas actually, the tendency of the person"},{"time":70000,"text":"is to be almost influenced"},{"time":73000,"text":"in absolute reverse proportion"},{"time":75000,"text":"to the amount of force being applied."},{"time":78000,"text":"So there seems to be a complete disconnect here."},{"time":80000,"text":"So what I'm asking for is the creation of a new job title --"},{"time":82000,"text":"I'll come to this a little later --"},{"time":84000,"text":"and perhaps the addition of a new word"},{"time":86000,"text":"into the English language."},{"time":88000,"text":"Because it does seem to me that large organizations"},{"time":91000,"text":"including government, which is, of course, the largest organization of all,"},{"time":94000,"text":"have actually become"},{"time":96000,"text":"completely disconnected"},{"time":98000,"text":"with what actually matters to people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":100000,"text":"Let me give you one example of this."},{"time":102000,"text":"You may remember this as the AOL-Time Warner merger, okay,"},{"time":106000,"text":"heralded at the time as the largest"},{"time":108000,"text":"single deal of all time."},{"time":110000,"text":"It may still be, for all I know."},{"time":112000,"text":"Now, all of you in this room, in one form or other,"},{"time":114000,"text":"are probably customers of one or both"},{"time":116000,"text":"of those organizations that merged."},{"time":118000,"text":"Just interested, did anybody notice anything different"},{"time":121000,"text":"as a result of this at all?"},{"time":123000,"text":"So unless you happened to be a shareholder"},{"time":125000,"text":"of one or the other organizations"},{"time":127000,"text":"or one of the dealmakers or lawyers involved in the no-doubt lucrative activity,"},{"time":130000,"text":"you're actually engaging in a huge piece of activity"},{"time":133000,"text":"that meant absolutely bugger-all to anybody, okay?"},{"time":137000,"text":"By contrast, years of marketing have taught me"},{"time":139000,"text":"that if you actually want people to remember you"},{"time":142000,"text":"and to appreciate what you do,"},{"time":144000,"text":"the most potent things are actually very, very small."},{"time":147000,"text":"This is from Virgin Atlantic upper-class,"},{"time":149000,"text":"it's the cruet salt and pepper set."},{"time":151000,"text":"Quite nice in itself, they're little, sort of, airplane things."},{"time":154000,"text":"What's really, really sweet is every single person looking at these things"},{"time":157000,"text":"has exactly the same mischievous thought,"},{"time":159000,"text":"which is, \"I reckon I can heist these.\""},{"time":162000,"text":"However, you pick them up and underneath,"},{"time":164000,"text":"actually engraved in the metal, are the words,"},{"time":166000,"text":"\"Stolen from Virgin Atlantic Airways upper-class.\""},{"time":169000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":171000,"text":"Now, years after"},{"time":173000,"text":"you remember the strategic question"},{"time":175000,"text":"of whether you're flying in a 777 or an Airbus,"},{"time":178000,"text":"you remember those words and that experience."}]},{"cues":[{"time":182000,"text":"Similarly, this is from a hotel in Stockholm, the Lydmar."},{"time":184000,"text":"Has anybody stayed there?"},{"time":186000,"text":"It's the lift, it's a series of buttons in the lift."},{"time":189000,"text":"Nothing unusual about that at all,"},{"time":192000,"text":"except that these are actually not the buttons that take you to an individual floor."},{"time":195000,"text":"It starts with garage at the bottom, I suppose, appropriately,"},{"time":198000,"text":"but it doesn't go up garage, grand floor, mezzanine, one, two, three, four."},{"time":201000,"text":"It actually says garage, funk, rhythm and blues."},{"time":205000,"text":"You have a series of buttons. You actually choose your lift music."},{"time":209000,"text":"My guess is that the cost of installing this in the lift"},{"time":212000,"text":"in the Lydmar Hotel in Stockholm"},{"time":214000,"text":"is probably 500 to 1,000 pounds max."},{"time":217000,"text":"It's frankly more memorable"},{"time":219000,"text":"than all those millions of hotels we've all stayed at"},{"time":222000,"text":"that tell you that your room has actually been recently renovated"},{"time":225000,"text":"at a cost of 500,000 dollars,"},{"time":227000,"text":"in order to make it resemble every other hotel room you've ever stayed in"},{"time":230000,"text":"in the entire course of your life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":234000,"text":"Now, these are trivial marketing examples, I accept."},{"time":237000,"text":"But I was at a TED event recently and Esther Duflo,"},{"time":240000,"text":"probably one of the leading experts in,"},{"time":242000,"text":"effectively, the eradication of poverty in the developing world,"},{"time":244000,"text":"actually spoke."},{"time":246000,"text":"And she came across a similar example"},{"time":248000,"text":"of something that fascinated me"},{"time":250000,"text":"as being something which, in a business context or a government context,"},{"time":253000,"text":"would simply be so trivial a solution"},{"time":255000,"text":"as to seem embarrassing."},{"time":257000,"text":"It was simply to encourage the inoculation of children"},{"time":260000,"text":"by, not only making it a social event --"},{"time":262000,"text":"I think good use of behavioral economics in that,"},{"time":264000,"text":"if you turn up with several other mothers"},{"time":266000,"text":"to have your child inoculated,"},{"time":268000,"text":"your sense of confidence is much greater than if you turn up alone."},{"time":271000,"text":"But secondly, to incentivize that inoculation"},{"time":273000,"text":"by giving a kilo of lentils to everybody who participated."},{"time":278000,"text":"It's a tiny, tiny thing."},{"time":280000,"text":"If you're a senior person at UNESCO"},{"time":283000,"text":"and someone says, \"So what are you doing"},{"time":285000,"text":"to eradicate world poverty?\""},{"time":287000,"text":"you're not really confident standing up there"},{"time":289000,"text":"saying, \"I've got it cracked; it's the lentils,\" are you?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":293000,"text":"Our own sense of self-aggrandizement"},{"time":295000,"text":"feels that big important problems"},{"time":297000,"text":"need to have big important, and most of all, expensive"},{"time":300000,"text":"solutions attached to them."},{"time":303000,"text":"And yet, what behavioral economics shows time after time after time"},{"time":306000,"text":"is in human behavioral and behavioral change"},{"time":308000,"text":"there's a very, very strong disproportionality at work,"},{"time":311000,"text":"that actually what changes our behavior"},{"time":314000,"text":"and what changes our attitude to things"},{"time":316000,"text":"is not actually proportionate to the degree"},{"time":318000,"text":"of expense entailed,"},{"time":320000,"text":"or the degree of force that's applied."},{"time":323000,"text":"But everything about institutions"},{"time":325000,"text":"makes them uncomfortable"},{"time":327000,"text":"with that disproportionality."},{"time":329000,"text":"So what happens in an institution"},{"time":331000,"text":"is the very person who has the power to solve the problem"},{"time":334000,"text":"also has a very, very large budget."},{"time":336000,"text":"And once you have a very, very large budget,"},{"time":338000,"text":"you actually look for expensive things to spend it on."},{"time":342000,"text":"What is completely lacking is a class of people"},{"time":344000,"text":"who have immense amounts of power, but no money at all."},{"time":347000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":349000,"text":"It's those people I'd quite like to create"},{"time":351000,"text":"in the world going forward."}]},{"cues":[{"time":353000,"text":"Now, here's another thing that happens,"},{"time":355000,"text":"which is what I call sometimes \"Terminal 5 syndrome,\""},{"time":357000,"text":"which is that big, expensive things"},{"time":359000,"text":"get big, highly-intelligent attention,"},{"time":362000,"text":"and they're great, and Terminal 5 is absolutely magnificent,"},{"time":365000,"text":"until you get down to the small detail, the usability,"},{"time":367000,"text":"which is the signage,"},{"time":369000,"text":"which is catastrophic."},{"time":371000,"text":"You come out of \"Arrive\" at the airport, and you follow"},{"time":373000,"text":"a big yellow sign that says \"Trains\" and it's in front of you."},{"time":376000,"text":"So you walk for another hundred yards,"},{"time":378000,"text":"expecting perhaps another sign,"},{"time":380000,"text":"that might courteously be yellow, in front of you and saying \"Trains.\""},{"time":383000,"text":"No, no, no, the next one is actually blue, to your left,"},{"time":385000,"text":"and says \"Heathrow Express.\""},{"time":387000,"text":"I mean, it could almost be rather like that scene from the film \"Airplane.\""},{"time":390000,"text":"A yellow sign? That's exactly what they'll be expecting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":393000,"text":"Actually, what happens in the world increasingly --"},{"time":395000,"text":"now, all credit to the British Airport Authority."},{"time":397000,"text":"I spoke about this before,"},{"time":399000,"text":"and a brilliant person got in touch with me and said, \"Okay, what can you do?\""},{"time":402000,"text":"So I did come up with five suggestions, which they are actually actioning."},{"time":405000,"text":"One of them also being,"},{"time":407000,"text":"although logically it's quite a good idea"},{"time":409000,"text":"to have a lift with no up and down button in it,"},{"time":411000,"text":"if it only serves two floors,"},{"time":413000,"text":"it's actually bloody terrifying, okay?"},{"time":416000,"text":"Because when the door closes"},{"time":418000,"text":"and there's nothing for you to do,"},{"time":420000,"text":"you've actually just stepped into a Hammer film."}]},{"cues":[{"time":422000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":424000,"text":"So these questions ... what is happening in the world"},{"time":426000,"text":"is the big stuff, actually,"},{"time":428000,"text":"is done magnificently well."},{"time":430000,"text":"But the small stuff, what you might call the user interface,"},{"time":433000,"text":"is done spectacularly badly."},{"time":435000,"text":"But also, there seems to be a complete sort of gridlock"},{"time":438000,"text":"in terms of solving these small solutions."},{"time":441000,"text":"Because the people who can actually solve them"},{"time":443000,"text":"actually are too powerful and too preoccupied"},{"time":445000,"text":"with something they think of as \"strategy\" to actually solve them."},{"time":448000,"text":"I tried this exercise recently, talking about banking."},{"time":450000,"text":"They said, \"Can we do an advertising campaign?"},{"time":452000,"text":"What can we do and encourage more online banking?\""},{"time":455000,"text":"I said, \"It's really, really easy.\""},{"time":457000,"text":"I said, \"When people login to their online bank"},{"time":459000,"text":"there are lots and lots of things they'd probably quite like to look at."},{"time":462000,"text":"The last thing in the world you ever want to see is your balance.\""},{"time":466000,"text":"I've got friends who actually"},{"time":468000,"text":"never use their own bank cash machines"},{"time":470000,"text":"because there's the risk that it might display"},{"time":472000,"text":"their balance on the screen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":474000,"text":"Why would you willingly expose yourself to bad news?"},{"time":477000,"text":"Okay, you simply wouldn't."},{"time":479000,"text":"I said, \"If you make, actually, 'Tell me my balance.'"},{"time":481000,"text":"If you make that an option rather than the default,"},{"time":484000,"text":"you'll find twice as many people log on to online banking,"},{"time":487000,"text":"and they do it three times as often.\""},{"time":489000,"text":"Let's face it, most of us -- how many of you"},{"time":491000,"text":"actually check your balance before you remove cash from a cash machine?"},{"time":495000,"text":"And you're pretty rich by the standards of the world at large."},{"time":498000,"text":"Now, interesting that no single person does that,"},{"time":500000,"text":"or at least can admit to being so anal as to do it."},{"time":504000,"text":"But what's interesting about that suggestion"},{"time":506000,"text":"was that, to implement that suggestion wouldn't cost 10 million pounds;"},{"time":509000,"text":"it wouldn't involve large amounts of expenditure;"},{"time":511000,"text":"it would actually cost about 50 quid."},{"time":513000,"text":"And yet, it never happens."}]},{"cues":[{"time":515000,"text":"Because there's a fundamental disconnect, as I said,"},{"time":518000,"text":"that actually, the people with the power"},{"time":520000,"text":"want to do big expensive things."},{"time":522000,"text":"And there's to some extent a big strategy myth"},{"time":524000,"text":"that's prevalent in business now."},{"time":526000,"text":"And if you think about it, it's very, very important"},{"time":528000,"text":"that the strategy myth is maintained."},{"time":530000,"text":"Because, if the board of directors convince everybody"},{"time":533000,"text":"that the success of any organization"},{"time":535000,"text":"is almost entirely dependent on the decisions made by the board of directors,"},{"time":538000,"text":"it makes the disparity in salaries"},{"time":541000,"text":"slightly more justifiable"},{"time":543000,"text":"than if you actually acknowledge that quite a lot of the credit for a company's success"},{"time":546000,"text":"might actually lie somewhere else,"},{"time":548000,"text":"in small pieces of tactical activity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":551000,"text":"But what is happening is that effectively --"},{"time":553000,"text":"and the invention of the spreadsheet hasn't helped this;"},{"time":555000,"text":"lots of things haven't helped this --"},{"time":557000,"text":"business and government suffers from a kind of physics envy."},{"time":560000,"text":"It wants the world to be the kind of place where"},{"time":563000,"text":"the input and the change are proportionate."},{"time":566000,"text":"It's a kind of mechanistic world"},{"time":568000,"text":"that we'd all love to live in"},{"time":570000,"text":"where, effectively, it sits very nicely on spreadsheets,"},{"time":573000,"text":"everything is numerically expressible,"},{"time":575000,"text":"and the amount you spend on something is proportionate"},{"time":578000,"text":"to the scale of your success."},{"time":580000,"text":"That's the world people actually want."},{"time":582000,"text":"In truth, we do live in a world that science can understand."},{"time":584000,"text":"Unfortunately, the science is probably closer to being climatology"},{"time":587000,"text":"in that in many cases,"},{"time":589000,"text":"very, very small changes"},{"time":591000,"text":"can have disproportionately huge effects,"},{"time":593000,"text":"and equally, vast areas of activity, enormous mergers,"},{"time":596000,"text":"can actually accomplish absolutely bugger-all."},{"time":600000,"text":"But it's very, very uncomfortable for us"},{"time":602000,"text":"to actually acknowledge that we're living in such a world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":605000,"text":"But what I'm saying is we could just make things"},{"time":607000,"text":"a little bit better for ourselves"},{"time":609000,"text":"if we looked at it in this very simple four-way approach."},{"time":613000,"text":"That is actually strategy, and I'm not denying that strategy has a role."},{"time":616000,"text":"You know, there are cases where you spend quite a lot of money"},{"time":618000,"text":"and you accomplish quite a lot."},{"time":620000,"text":"And I'd be wrong to dis that completely."},{"time":623000,"text":"Moving over, we come, of course, to consultancy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":625000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":629000,"text":"I thought it was very indecent of Accenture"},{"time":631000,"text":"to ditch Tiger Woods in such"},{"time":633000,"text":"a sort of hurried and hasty way."},{"time":635000,"text":"I mean, Tiger surely was actually obeying the Accenture model."},{"time":638000,"text":"He developed an interesting outsourcing model for sexual services,"},{"time":641000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":643000,"text":"no longer tied to a single monopoly provider,"},{"time":646000,"text":"in many cases, sourcing things locally,"},{"time":649000,"text":"and of course, the ability to have between one and three girls delivered at any time"},{"time":652000,"text":"led for better load-balancing."},{"time":655000,"text":"So what Accenture suddenly found so unattractive about that, I'm not sure."}]},{"cues":[{"time":658000,"text":"Then there are other things that don't cost much and achieve absolutely nothing."},{"time":661000,"text":"That's called trivia."},{"time":663000,"text":"But there's a fourth thing."},{"time":665000,"text":"And the fundamental problem is we don't actually have a word for this stuff."},{"time":668000,"text":"We don't know what to call it."},{"time":670000,"text":"And actually we don't spend nearly enough money"},{"time":673000,"text":"looking for those things,"},{"time":675000,"text":"looking for those tiny things that may or may not work,"},{"time":678000,"text":"but which, if they do work,"},{"time":680000,"text":"can have a success absolutely out of proportion"},{"time":682000,"text":"to their expense, their efforts"},{"time":684000,"text":"and the disruption they cause."}]},{"cues":[{"time":686000,"text":"So the first thing I'd like"},{"time":688000,"text":"is a competition -- to anybody watching this as a film --"},{"time":690000,"text":"is to come up with a name for that stuff on the bottom right."},{"time":693000,"text":"And the second thing, I think,"},{"time":695000,"text":"is that the world needs to have people in charge of that."},{"time":697000,"text":"That's why I call for the \"Chief Detail Officer.\""},{"time":699000,"text":"Every corporation should have one,"},{"time":701000,"text":"and every government should have a Ministry of Detail."},{"time":704000,"text":"The people who actually have no money,"},{"time":706000,"text":"who have no extravagant budget,"},{"time":708000,"text":"but who realize that actually"},{"time":710000,"text":"you might achieve greater success in uptake"},{"time":712000,"text":"of a government program"},{"time":714000,"text":"by actually doubling the level of benefits you pay,"},{"time":716000,"text":"but you'll probably achieve exactly that same effect"},{"time":719000,"text":"simply by redesigning the form"},{"time":721000,"text":"and writing it in comprehensible English."},{"time":723000,"text":"And if actually we created a Ministry of Detail"},{"time":726000,"text":"and business actually had Chief Detail Officers,"},{"time":728000,"text":"then that fourth quadrant,"},{"time":730000,"text":"which is so woefully neglected at the moment,"},{"time":732000,"text":"might finally get the attention it deserves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":734000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]}]}